727815f-c.text:
Queens Boulevard, south side, opposite 65th Road, showing three views of the Geo. Englard house formerly known as 830 Queens Boulevard. This house which was demolished in March 1925, was erected by the above individual on the site of an older house
that was demolished by fire.
April 1923
Views 1 and 2
View 3: February 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
